"""Test get_ficon_port_thread_stats."""
response = self.perf.get_ficon_port_thread_stats(ficon_port_thread_id=self.
    p_data.ficon_port_thread_id, metrics=pc.KPI, start_time=self.time_now,
    end_time=self.time_now)
self.assertIsInstance(response, dict)
self.assertEqual(response.get('reporting_level'), self.common.
    convert_to_snake_case(pc.FICON_PORT_THR))
